00:01:36,897 --> 00:01:37,931
Heil Hitler!

3
00:01:43,996 --> 00:01:44,996
Heil Hitler!

4
00:01:47,791 --> 00:01:50,736
-In your opinion Herr Dr 
-He's been talking too much

5
