why didn't you jam them out?

787
00:47:18,336 --> 00:47:20,713
If we jam them,Sir,
the detectors can't find them

788
00:47:20,713 --> 00:47:22,690
Well they are not rounded 
up in a couple of days

789
00:47:22,748 --> 00:47:24,091
 your job won't allow 2 pfennigs

790
00:47:24,091 --> 00:47:26,469
Our detectors can locate them in 22 seconds

791
00:47:26,469 --> 00:47:28,904
We'll get them tomorrow night as 
soon as they start their broadcasting

792
00:47:28,913 --> 00:47:29,913
You'd better

793
00:47:31,349 --> 00:47:32,949
Herr Spiedler talking

794
00:47:33,642 --> 00:47:39,398
Yes,tell the Herr doctor,I rang up to 
wish him many happy returns of the day

795
00:47:39,398 --> 00:47:45,654
Well,would you wish Dr Roeder many 
happy returns of the day from Maria

796
00:47:45,746 --> 00:47:46,989
Will you wish Dr Roeder

797
00:47:46,989 --> 00:47:49,909
many happy returns of the day 
from his friend in East Prussia

798
00:47:50,451 --> 00:47:53,412
I'll tell him Sir,but I'm sure 
there is some mistake

799
00:47:54,172 --> 00:47:56,916
-Oh,doctor,
-Help yourself to a drink,boys

800
00:47:57,592 --> 00:48:00,127
Doctor,the telephone hasn't 
stop ringing since half past ten

801
00:48:00,127 --> 00:48:01,203
What do they want?

802
00:48:01,203 --> 00:48:02,713
I think someone is telling a joke

803
00:48:02,713 --> 00:48:04,799
They'll be calling up from 
all over the country

804
00:48:04,799 --> 00:48:06,799
wishing you many happy returns

805
00:48:07,385 --> 00:48:09,303
I told them that it wasn't your birthday

806
00:48:13,232 --> 00:48:15,935
Well,boys,all over the country

807
00:48:16,844 --> 00:48:17,937
We've done it

808
00:48:18,896 --> 00:48:19,896
-Doctor
-Doctor

809
00:48:31,075 --> 00:48:33,077
-Well
-They're due to start in about a minute,Sir

810
00:48:33,161 --> 00:48:35,413
As soon as they do we'll find 
their position on this map

811
00:48:35,413 --> 00:48:36,472
-Nagel
-Sir?

812
00:48:36,472 --> 00:48:38,048
Just explain to Herr Rabenau,will you

813
00:48:38,048 --> 00:48:39,642
We pick up the waves from Freedom radio

814
00:48:39,642 --> 00:48:41,627
on detectors placed about 200 miles apart

815
00:48:41,627 --> 00:48:44,505
For example Berlin and Breslau

816
00:48:45,673 --> 00:48:47,550
By taking the maximum 
intensity of these waves

817
00:48:47,550 --> 00:48:48,717
each of these stations

818
00:48:48,717 --> 00:48:50,502
can get the direction of the pirate station

819
00:48:50,502 --> 00:48:51,895
in relations to their own position

820
00:48:51,895 --> 00:48:53,681
and where these two direction intersect

821
00:48:53,681 --> 00:48:55,891
is the rough position 
of the pirate transmitter

822
00:48:56,892 --> 00:48:58,102
How exactly do you do that?

823
00:48:58,102 --> 00:48:59,770
Do you see that instrument over there,Sir

824
00:49:00,062 --> 00:49:01,062
Let me explain

825
00:49:04,024 --> 00:49:06,068
That's what we call a directive aerial

826
00:49:06,444 --> 00:49:08,904
This man finds the direction 
of maximum intensity

827
00:49:08,904 --> 00:49:10,197
from the freedom station

828
00:49:10,448 --> 00:49:12,575
Meanwhile we receive a reading from Breslau

829
00:49:12,575 --> 00:49:14,702
by plotting both these readings on the map

830
00:49:14,702 --> 00:49:17,163
as you saw obtain the point of intersection

831
00:49:17,788 --> 00:49:20,583
This is the freedom station 
calling on short wave 26.9

832
00:49:20,583 --> 00:49:24,615
"There we are going to take up 
some problems that affects us all"

833
00:49:24,753 --> 00:49:30,009
-There's your blib
-Breslau bearing 95 degree east

834
00:49:30,593 --> 00:49:32,052
Breslau 95 degrees West

835
00:49:37,066 --> 00:49:38,751
It's someone in Ostertal district,Sir

836
00:49:39,852 --> 00:49:44,023
Squad car attention stop 
all traffic entering city from North

837
00:49:44,773 --> 00:49:46,692
Search for radio transmitter

838
00:49:47,276 --> 00:49:50,863
-About a mile northeast of Ostertahl
-About a mile northeast of Ostertahl

839
00:49:51,280 --> 00:49:54,283
Ostertahl,it's about 12 miles from here

840
00:49:55,451 --> 00:49:56,869
Just coming into Ostertahl

841
00:50:13,636 --> 00:50:16,931
-That's the peak South 21 West 14
-South 21 West 14

842
00:50:18,849 --> 00:50:20,049
North 2 West 28

843
00:50:23,988 --> 00:50:25,481
We are doing everything we can Sir

844
00:50:25,581 --> 00:50:27,900
I got all my best men working day and night

845
00:50:50,514 --> 00:50:51,514
Karl

846
00:50:52,675 --> 00:50:53,955
It's almost time

847
00:50:55,803 --> 00:50:56,803
Ready to go

848
00:50:59,723 --> 00:51:00,723
Right

849
00:51:20,578 --> 00:51:22,371
-Ready?
-Just about

850
00:51:27,451 --> 00:51:28,752
There you are Professor

851
00:51:28,853 --> 00:51:30,154
This is  freedom station message

852
00:51:35,301 --> 00:51:35,718
Right

853
00:51:36,844 --> 00:51:40,598
This is a freedom station 
calling on wavelength 26.9

854
00:51:42,433 --> 00:51:43,767
I'll tell you we must find them

855
00:51:45,311 --> 00:51:47,521
I had another call from 
Berchtesgarden this morning

856
00:51:48,355 --> 00:51:50,649
How can I find them if Goebbels 
keeps jamming them out

857
00:51:51,775 --> 00:51:53,277
Now we have absolute proof

858
00:51:54,153 --> 00:51:58,157
that your criminal leaders are investing 
millions of marks in foreign securities

859
00:51:59,074 --> 00:52:02,244
Here are the figures everyone 
of them has been verified

860
00:52:02,244 --> 00:52:05,831
Rabenau who presumes to tell you

861
00:52:05,831 --> 00:52:07,791
 to turn your butter into guns

862
00:52:07,791 --> 00:52:10,419
has the depositions in 
the following sums abroad

863
00:52:10,419 --> 00:52:16,050
Buenos Aires 7,5 million marks 
in Luxemburg 2 million

864
00:52:16,800 --> 00:52:18,260
That wasn't jammed was it?

865
00:52:19,595 --> 00:52:22,806
Muller,you occupy a position
of responsibility

866
00:52:23,041 --> 00:52:25,209
So far you've been lucky 
enough to keep that position

867
00:52:26,268 --> 00:52:28,812
The third Reich does not tolerate failures

868
00:52:29,638 --> 00:52:31,106
I think you understand me

869
00:52:33,525 --> 00:52:35,277
Well,that's the list

870
00:52:35,819 --> 00:52:37,446
Something to think about isn't it?

871
00:52:37,889 --> 00:52:39,390
How long are we going to put up with

872
00:52:39,490 --> 00:52:43,243
this whole scale thieving of 
public funds by our ministers of state

873
00:52:49,792 --> 00:52:52,628
Hanna it's Karl,he's come back

874
00:52:54,963 --> 00:52:57,716
What swollen dreams do 
you suppose these men hold

875
00:52:58,717 --> 00:53:03,263
while you at the same time 
hold death and misery for you,the people

876
00:53:07,017 --> 00:53:08,017
How funny

877
00:53:08,143 --> 00:53:10,187
-I thought for a minute that was
-Karl

878
00:53:11,097 --> 00:53:12,106
Yes

879
00:53:12,773 --> 00:53:13,899
That was the freedom radio

880
00:53:16,151 --> 00:53:17,403
Ridiculous

881
00:53:18,237 --> 00:53:20,072
Must be some resemblance in the voice

882
00:53:20,072 --> 00:53:21,824
Quite a strong resemblance I'd thought

883
00:53:24,210 --> 00:53:25,269
Don't be stupid Otto

884
00:53:29,248 --> 00:53:30,248
Hanna

885
00:53:31,125 --> 00:53:32,710
All right duckie, I'm just getting them

886
00:53:34,002 --> 00:53:35,337
Well I must be off

887
00:53:35,846 --> 00:53:37,172
Aren't you going to wait for me?

888
00:53:37,756 --> 00:53:40,509
I'm afraid I can't do it,
there's a job I must do

889
00:53:41,802 --> 00:53:42,803
I'll be home later

890
00:53:43,053 --> 00:53:44,346
All right good night

891
00:53:47,908 --> 00:53:49,143
She seemed to note it at once

892
00:53:49,143 --> 00:53:51,979
she actually called out his name
when she opened the door

893
00:53:51,979 --> 00:53:55,023
You don't like Dr Roeder very much,do you?

894
00:53:55,566 --> 00:53:57,960
It's not that,Sir,I thought it 
was my duty to tell you

895
00:53:59,153 --> 00:54:00,279
It was indeed

896
00:54:01,071 --> 00:54:02,239
You've done very well my boy

897
00:54:02,698 --> 00:54:05,868
I'm just wondering if we can't make 
more use of your special advantages

898
00:54:05,968 --> 00:54:08,704
What about taking him 
into your detection unit,Muller

899
00:54:09,180 --> 00:54:10,522
I'll be very glad to have him,Sir

900
00:54:10,973 --> 00:54:11,999
Thank you,Sir

901
00:54:11,999 --> 00:54:14,168
Report to Capt Muller's 
office in the morning

902
00:54:15,127 --> 00:54:17,296
-Heil Hitler
-Heil Hitler

903
00:54:21,133 --> 00:54:22,968
Well,that's a very pretty surprise

904
00:54:22,968 --> 00:54:24,152
You're going to arrest Roeder?

905
00:54:24,152 --> 00:54:26,847
No, we need more evidence 
than to arrest the Fuhrer's doctor

906
00:54:26,847 --> 00:54:28,515
besides we want the others too

907
00:54:29,308 --> 00:54:31,435
I'm going to give a 
little party at my house

908
00:54:32,144 --> 00:54:33,812
Dr Roeder should be the guest of honor

909
00:54:33,979 --> 00:54:35,647
-He'd smell a rat
-That's the idea

910
00:54:36,607 --> 00:54:39,610
Suppose we ask him for 1015 
just before the broadcast

911
00:54:40,444 --> 00:54:42,988
-I'll ask her too
-I thought they weren't living together

912
00:54:42,988 --> 00:54:44,047
They are not

913
00:54:44,823 --> 00:54:46,950
Her reaction should be very entertaining

914
00:54:51,288 --> 00:54:53,540
Irena it's your turn now

915
00:54:53,957 --> 00:54:55,959
-Won't you please do something?
-No -Oh,please do

916
00:54:59,129 --> 00:55:01,924
You really must let me off tonight
I've been at the stadium all day

917
00:55:02,382 --> 00:55:05,010
What little surprise have 
you got in stall for us this time

918
00:55:05,010 --> 00:55:06,929
One that I think ought to be rather good

919
00:55:06,929 --> 00:55:11,217
when the Fuhrer comes in a 140 
foot banners were unfurl in the wind

920
00:55:12,100 --> 00:55:16,063
Which reminds me really I 
don't think I ordered the wind

921
00:55:16,146 --> 00:55:17,314
I'll talk to Goebbels

922
00:55:17,314 --> 00:55:18,398
We don't want a hurricane

923
00:55:18,398 --> 00:55:21,360
you know when our good 
doctors exaggerate things

924
00:55:22,277 --> 00:55:25,030
There was a message from 
Karl,he's been delayed at the clinic

925
00:55:25,030 --> 00:55:27,323
He'll be along later

926
00:55:27,574 --> 00:55:30,869
BTW the so called freedom 
station is on the air just now

927
00:55:30,869 --> 00:55:33,038
might be amusing to hear 
what they have to say

928
00:55:33,038 --> 00:55:34,038
Yes

929
00:55:36,458 --> 00:55:39,086
I don't think we shall 
have any more opportunities

930
00:55:40,587 --> 00:55:42,464
"And tonight the minister of propaganda

931
00:55:42,464 --> 00:55:44,132
has once more been telling you

932
00:55:44,132 --> 00:55:47,010
that our envious neighbor
 are preparing to invade Germany

933
00:55:47,010 --> 00:55:50,264
and destroy her people that too is a lie"

934
00:55:51,473 --> 00:55:54,476
Invented to excuse preparations "

935
00:55:54,476 --> 00:55:56,343
I won't listen to that stuff

936
00:55:56,370 --> 00:55:58,689
Oh quite,but there is 
something about that voice

937
00:55:58,689 --> 00:56:01,108
Oh yes,do let's hear 
some more,it's so thrilling

938
00:56:01,191 --> 00:56:02,200
Please

939
00:56:03,911 --> 00:56:05,612
I'm sorry Karl missed that

940
00:56:05,612 --> 00:56:07,573
As he might have found it amusing

941
00:56:09,449 --> 00:56:10,569
Sorry I'm late,Willie

942
00:56:14,288 --> 00:56:15,455
Oh hello Karl

943
00:56:27,843 --> 00:56:29,845
Listen tomorrow 
night at 10 30 as usual

944
00:56:29,845 --> 00:56:34,641
Tell your friends to tune in 
on wave length 26.9 meters

945
00:56:34,641 --> 00:56:37,811
And in the mean time,good night

946
00:56:43,559 --> 00:56:44,818
Let me help you

947
00:56:50,366 --> 00:56:51,366
Thank you

948
00:56:52,367 --> 00:56:53,647
Good night,Irena

949
00:56:55,838 --> 00:56:57,247
Won't you see me home?

950
00:56:59,166 --> 00:57:00,208
Of course

951
00:57:07,090 --> 00:57:08,342
Well,there's one thing

952
00:57:08,342 --> 00:57:10,928
we can take Roeder off the list 
and start looking elsewhere

953
00:57:10,928 --> 00:57:14,222
On the contrary we can 
now concentrate on Roeder

954
00:57:16,266 --> 00:57:18,268
Very easy to put a voice 
on a gramophone record

955
00:57:18,268 --> 00:57:20,395
but very hard to conceal the scratch

956
00:57:22,689 --> 00:57:26,401
-You've been busy at the stadium?
-What? Oh,yes

957
00:57:27,694 --> 00:57:29,404
-Must be very interesting
-Very

958
00:57:29,821 --> 00:57:32,032
-Will you be there?
-No,I'm afraid not

959
00:57:32,032 --> 00:57:34,201
I shall be busy at the clinic

960
00:57:37,329 --> 00:57:38,538
Been a long time hasn't it?

961
00:57:38,538 --> 00:57:39,538
Yes

962
00:57:41,408 --> 00:57:42,501
Have you missed me?

963
00:57:45,153 --> 00:57:46,213
What do you think?

964
00:57:47,589 --> 00:57:48,589
Oh,Karl

965
00:57:49,633 --> 00:57:51,885
Why do we go on like this
isn't it rather silly?

966
00:57:54,146 --> 00:57:55,555
I'm not enjoying it,Irena

967
00:57:56,473 --> 00:57:57,724
Can't we try again?

968
00:57:58,475 --> 00:58:01,353
We've both been made miserable 
for no good reason

969
00:58:02,145 --> 00:58:03,939
I'd give a lot to be convinced of that

970
00:58:03,939 --> 00:58:05,065
Oh,Karl,

971
00:58:06,400 --> 00:58:08,402
Nothing is big enough to 
make us suffer like this

972
00:58:08,402 --> 00:58:09,820
it doesn't make sense

973
00:58:10,162 --> 00:58:11,488
Will you go back on your belief?

974
00:58:12,739 --> 00:58:14,408
The fuhrer and all he stands for?

975
00:58:14,408 --> 00:58:17,744
How can I? How we agree 
to differ about politics

976
00:58:17,744 --> 00:58:19,413
Politics? It is something deeper than that

977
00:58:19,413 --> 00:58:21,657
I feel it so strongly

978
00:58:23,417 --> 00:58:25,460
Oh let's talk about something else

979
00:58:26,003 --> 00:58:27,003
Oh,Karl

980
00:58:29,214 --> 00:58:32,926
What ever you feel need it 
stop us loving each other

981
00:58:34,052 --> 00:58:35,804
As far as I am concerned it never will

982
00:58:37,514 --> 00:58:39,141
That what makes it so hard

983
00:58:39,808 --> 00:58:40,851
Even to talk to you

984
00:58:41,802 --> 00:58:42,894
You see

985
00:58:43,854 --> 00:58:47,232
I don't feel like I've the 
right go back on what I've said

986
00:58:48,726 --> 00:58:49,776
Even if I wanted to

987
00:58:51,820 --> 00:58:52,988
Not even if I ask you

988
00:58:54,289 --> 00:58:55,323
Sorry

989
00:58:56,208 --> 00:58:57,617
Not even if you ask me

990
00:59:00,028 --> 00:59:01,121
I see

991
00:59:03,790 --> 00:59:05,125
Taxi

992
00:59:11,081 --> 00:59:12,174
Pariser Platz

993
00:59:14,176 --> 00:59:15,635
-Good night
-Good night

994
00:59:26,188 --> 00:59:28,315
Attention everyone,attention everyone

995
00:59:28,690 --> 00:59:32,402
On Monday our fuhrer will speak 
to us from the Tempelhof's stadium

996
00:59:32,402 --> 00:59:33,445
On the peace of Europe

997
00:59:33,445 --> 00:59:35,030
Every German will listen

998
00:59:35,697 --> 00:59:38,784
Work will cease at six o'clock 
in all factories and offices

999
00:59:38,784 --> 00:59:40,327
Children will assembly in schools

1000
00:59:41,244 --> 00:59:44,456
Peace of Europe,80 million people 
forced to listen to lies like that

1001
00:59:44,456 --> 00:59:46,666
You can shouting the truth 
at them for seven months

1002
00:59:46,666 --> 00:59:48,168
and I don't suppose we'll reach 20 %

1003
00:59:48,477 --> 00:59:49,861
Sorry in my opinion you never will

1004
00:59:49,861 --> 00:59:50,937
And why not?

1005
00:59:50,937 --> 00:59:52,939
Because there are too many 
people like you moaning

1006
00:59:52,939 --> 00:59:54,015
and nothing can be done

1007
00:59:54,015 --> 00:59:54,757
Can't see what can be done?

1008
00:59:54,757 --> 00:59:56,885
They like giving orders or taking 
orders I know the German mentality

1009
00:59:56,885 --> 00:59:58,178
Damned Rudolph our fellows are German

1010
00:59:58,178 --> 01:00:00,180
Hans and Kurt are Germans 
they are not unique

1011
01:00:00,314 --> 01:00:01,640
They are not many of then

1012
01:00:05,402 --> 01:00:06,478
Hello

1013
01:00:06,478 --> 01:00:10,607
I just want to tell you the 
appointment this one next Friday

1014
01:00:12,484 --> 01:00:13,484
Thank you

1015
01:00:18,598 --> 01:00:19,658
What is it?

1016
01:00:21,326 --> 01:00:22,702
That was Wolfgang

1017
01:00:22,702 --> 01:00:25,330
They invade Poland on Friday

1018
01:00:33,130 --> 01:00:34,381
Friday

1019
01:00:35,249 --> 01:00:36,324
Five days

1020
01:00:36,442 --> 01:00:39,886
I told you,you are up 
against something too big

1021
01:00:40,579 --> 01:00:41,596
Nothing too big

1022
01:00:44,182 --> 01:00:45,892
Landbach thought it was worthwhile

1023
01:00:47,602 --> 01:00:50,772
-Didn't stop him
-No but they broke his neck

1024
01:00:52,399 --> 01:00:53,441
Now listen Karl

1025
01:00:53,441 --> 01:00:55,986
you're doing great work as a doctor

1026
01:00:56,536 --> 01:00:57,737
don't throw it away

1027
01:00:58,964 --> 01:01:00,657
You can still lead a useful and happy life

1028
01:01:02,033 --> 01:01:05,412
With all this unhappiness,no Rudolph

1029
01:01:07,539 --> 01:01:09,040
The invasion on Friday

1030
01:01:10,000 --> 01:01:11,793
Peace speech on Tuesday

1031
01:01:13,086 --> 01:01:15,755
The whole of Germany forced to listen

1032
01:01:17,716 --> 01:01:19,217
The whole of Germany

1033
01:01:20,769 --> 01:01:21,803
I wonder

1034
01:01:38,779 --> 01:01:40,597
-Hello Karl
-Hello Emil,Fritz-Good evening,Sir

1035
01:01:43,283 --> 01:01:44,743
Got anything to drink?

1036
01:01:46,161 --> 01:01:48,205
I always thought stars 
dressing room was full of it

1037
01:01:48,622 --> 01:01:49,789
-Full of what?
-Drink

1038
01:01:51,558 --> 01:01:53,360
Oh,Fritz get the doctor some beer,will you?

1039
01:01:53,427 --> 01:01:55,445
It only be your number
in a minute and quarter,Sir

1040
01:01:55,445 --> 01:01:56,863
I'll look after Mr Fenner,Fritz

1041
01:01:59,391 --> 01:02:01,368
You're always saying 
what a good driver you are

1042
01:02:02,752 --> 01:02:04,395
Now you have an opportunity of proving it

1043
01:02:04,447 --> 01:02:05,505
What?

1044
01:02:05,539 --> 01:02:06,848
You're to be at Taeppische car park

1045
01:02:06,948 --> 01:02:08,881
at stadium tomorrow 5 o'clock

1046
01:02:09,609 --> 01:02:11,311
You mean you're actually going to try?

1047
01:02:12,646 --> 01:02:13,713
Why not?

1048
01:02:16,583 --> 01:02:18,485
That shocking stuff you're 
putting on your skin

1049
01:02:19,402 --> 01:02:20,779
Takes ten years off my age

1050
01:02:22,840 --> 01:02:23,907
You know,Karl

1051
01:02:24,908 --> 01:02:26,868
You deserve to succeed

1052
01:02:28,295 --> 01:02:30,872
You put ten years on your age 
if you plug up your skin with that

1053
01:02:31,189 --> 01:02:32,207
Coat

1054
01:02:34,634 --> 01:02:36,586
The moment the fuhrer starts his speech

1055
01:02:37,345 --> 01:02:38,380
You get your engine going

1056
01:02:38,831 --> 01:02:39,839
I've got your pass

1057
01:02:39,873 --> 01:02:40,940
Here it is

1058
01:02:43,218 --> 01:02:45,136
Emil,I can count on you?

1059
01:02:45,887 --> 01:02:47,097
Your call Mr Fenner

1060
01:02:47,123 --> 01:02:48,289
Right

1061
01:02:49,775 --> 01:02:50,850
Umbrella

1062
01:02:53,128 --> 01:02:54,354
Bye Karl

1063
01:03:09,937 --> 01:03:10,937
Heil

1064
01:03:28,888 --> 01:03:29,888
Heil Hitler

1065
01:03:38,690 --> 01:03:41,359
-What do you want?
-Last minute inspection of cables

1066
01:03:43,111 --> 01:03:45,196
If anything goes wrong 
tonight I should lose my job

1067
01:03:45,613 --> 01:03:46,781
You might lose more than that

1068
01:03:48,950 --> 01:03:49,950
Open that bag

1069
01:03:53,421 --> 01:03:54,456
What's that?

1070
01:03:56,291 --> 01:03:58,168
A bomb what do you think?

1071
01:04:02,464 --> 01:04:03,798
-Heil Hitler
-Heil Hitler

1072
01:04:51,263 --> 01:04:52,347
What's this?

1073
01:04:57,185 --> 01:04:58,269
Auxiliary line

1074
01:05:00,380 --> 01:05:01,439
Show me that box

1075
01:05:24,479 --> 01:05:25,547
Help

1076
01:05:55,493 --> 01:05:56,578
Thanks

1077
01:05:57,837 --> 01:05:58,913
Better tie him up

1078
01:06:18,099 --> 01:06:19,767
-The fuhrer
-Right

1079
01:06:36,576 --> 01:06:39,954
Such a magnificent arena,
I congratulate you

1080
01:06:40,747 --> 01:06:42,332
I must say it's looks rather good

1081
01:06:47,545 --> 01:06:50,590
-Where have you been?
-Sorry,Sir,I was checking up the front gates

1082
01:07:02,769 --> 01:07:05,605
German men and German women

1083
01:07:07,732 --> 01:07:10,276
"The soldier who sometimes 
wear civilian clothes"

1084
01:07:11,653 --> 01:07:14,781
-Good luck,Karl
-Thank you,Maria

1085
01:07:19,452 --> 01:07:22,413
"On the ruins of the infamous 
treaty of Versailles"

1086
01:07:23,039 --> 01:07:26,042
"A new proud Germany has arisen"

1087
01:07:27,085 --> 01:07:31,297
And the challenge of our 
youth we'll no longer deny"

1088
01:07:34,217 --> 01:07:36,469
"That is the watchword of my policy"

1089
01:07:37,929 --> 01:07:39,013
"Peace is might"

1090
01:07:39,639 --> 01:07:44,185
"Peace for Germany and for...."

1091
01:07:47,188 --> 01:07:48,606
"That is a lie"

1092
01:07:48,606 --> 01:07:51,442
"This is the freedom station 
calling on Short wave 26.9"

1093
01:07:51,442 --> 01:07:53,695
"You face the greatest 
moment in your history"

1094
01:07:53,945 --> 01:07:56,155
"Tonight at 10 30 we shall 
make a vital announcement"

1095
01:07:56,155 --> 01:07:57,523
"All I have time to tell you now"

1096
01:07:57,623 --> 01:07:59,701
"is that the fuhrer far 
from working for peace"

1097
01:07:59,701 --> 01:08:01,286
" is about to commit you to war"

1098
01:08:01,828 --> 01:08:03,329
"We believe one more time.."

1099
01:08:06,874 --> 01:08:09,794
"War can only end with the
 annihilation of Germany"

1100
01:08:20,505 --> 01:08:21,764
No one is allowed through here

1101
01:08:22,174 --> 01:08:23,224
Now get back

1102
01:08:28,271 --> 01:08:30,064
-Where are you going?
-Special job,Sir

1103
01:08:30,156 --> 01:08:32,150
No one is allowed to leave,
show me your papers

1104
01:09:22,784 --> 01:09:25,870
Double bend ahead,when 
we get round,you jump out

1105
01:09:26,404 --> 01:09:27,470
No

1106
01:09:28,406 --> 01:09:29,540
Do as I tell you

1107
01:10:10,532 --> 01:10:11,541
Hello

1108
01:10:11,741 --> 01:10:13,751
Not yet I'm not a thought reader

1109
01:10:15,503 --> 01:10:16,504
You didn't see who it was

1110
01:10:16,504 --> 01:10:20,133
No,Sir,I had the mechanic down 
and my back to the door

1111
01:10:20,133 --> 01:10:21,192
Whoever it was

1112
01:10:21,192 --> 01:10:24,169
must have been in the corridor,
you must have seen him before you went in

1113
01:10:24,221 --> 01:10:25,972
There was no one there,Sir

1114
01:10:26,973 --> 01:10:28,307
Herr Dressler will tell you,Sir

1115
01:10:28,933 --> 01:10:30,476
I thought you went for the main gates

1116
01:10:31,352 --> 01:10:34,105
Yes,Sir but I came back that way

1117
01:10:41,529 --> 01:10:42,697
I want you again later

1118
01:10:43,181 --> 01:10:44,240
Yes,Sir

1119
01:10:52,315 --> 01:10:53,332
Hello,hello

1120
01:10:54,125 --> 01:10:55,418
Muller where the devil

1121
01:10:55,793 --> 01:10:56,793
What?

1122
01:10:57,962 --> 01:10:58,963
Where about?

1123
01:10:59,213 --> 01:11:00,923
A street where Roeder has his clinic

1124
01:11:01,257 --> 01:11:04,135
Yes,we're throwing a cordon 
on the entire block

1125
01:11:04,886 --> 01:11:06,053
Right away

1126
01:11:23,271 --> 01:11:24,280
Halt

1127
01:11:25,782 --> 01:11:27,950
Schulz,take a room in there and search it

1128
01:11:28,743 --> 01:11:30,369
Kalder,in there

1129
01:11:32,079 --> 01:11:32,955
Lt

1130
01:11:33,590 --> 01:11:35,066
You know Dr Roeder's private rooms?

1131
01:11:35,243 --> 01:11:36,984
Go around behind them and a thorough search

1132
01:11:37,060 --> 01:11:38,461
-take these men with you
-Come on

1133
01:11:39,170 --> 01:11:40,254
You'll come with me

1134
01:11:40,254 --> 01:11:41,614
What do you want?

1135
01:11:41,622 --> 01:11:42,956
I wish to see Dr Roeder at once

1136
01:11:42,956 --> 01:11:44,274
You can't he's with his patients

1137
01:11:44,274 --> 01:11:45,593
-In there
-You can't I tell you

1138
01:11:50,156 --> 01:11:52,475
What the devil do you mean 
by bursting in here like this?

1139
01:11:54,011 --> 01:11:56,629
I've orders to search this building 
for a wireless transmitter

1140
01:11:57,071 --> 01:11:59,565
This is a clinic,not a broadcasting station

1141
01:11:59,565 --> 01:12:00,733
Is it?

1142
01:12:01,651 --> 01:12:02,693
What's that?

1143
01:12:19,168 --> 01:12:21,462
Who are you,what do you want?

1144
01:12:46,696 --> 01:12:47,738
Hans

1145
01:12:50,283 --> 01:12:51,283
Elly

1146
01:12:56,080 --> 01:12:57,331
What's the matter?

1147
01:12:57,732 --> 01:12:58,749
What's happened?

1148
01:13:01,127 --> 01:13:02,253
I've been ill

1149
01:13:03,963 --> 01:13:05,006
I couldn't do the work

1150
01:13:05,832 --> 01:13:06,841
Work?

1151
01:13:07,717 --> 01:13:09,427
Food was so bad

1152
01:13:10,244 --> 01:13:11,304
I couldn't eat it

1153
01:13:13,180 --> 01:13:14,307
I got away

1154
01:13:14,640 --> 01:13:16,267
But your letters?

1155
01:13:17,768 --> 01:13:19,770
We only wrote what we were told

1156
01:13:20,738 --> 01:13:22,481
Look here,what sort of rest home was this?

1157
01:13:24,984 --> 01:13:26,402
It wasn't a rest home

1158
01:13:29,280 --> 01:13:31,490
It was a concentration camp

1159
01:13:32,575 --> 01:13:34,410
Concentration camp

1160
01:13:37,455 --> 01:13:38,998
I can't go back there,Hans

1161
01:13:40,166 --> 01:13:42,126
I can't go back there

1162
01:13:45,221 --> 01:13:47,381
Concentration camp

1163
01:13:49,634 --> 01:13:50,968
I'm sorry you can't go through

1164
01:13:50,968 --> 01:13:52,511
But I'm Frau Roeder

1165
01:13:52,511 --> 01:13:54,046
I can't help that but you can't go in

1166
01:13:54,130 --> 01:13:56,307
It's quite all right,of course,
Frau Roeder can go in

1167
01:13:57,767 --> 01:13:58,776
Thank you

1168
01:14:02,271 --> 01:14:03,271
Shall I open,Sir?

1169
01:14:05,491 --> 01:14:06,567
Yes go ahead

1170
01:14:12,206 --> 01:14:13,206
Carry on

1171
01:14:16,678 --> 01:14:17,745
Not at all

1172
01:14:19,664 --> 01:14:20,773
In difficulties?

1173
01:14:22,833 --> 01:14:23,833
Allow me

1174
01:14:24,719 --> 01:14:25,736
I had orders to search

1175
01:14:27,213 --> 01:14:28,589
Quite I just want to help

1176
01:14:31,676 --> 01:14:34,929
Here,you might call this my private museum

1177
01:14:36,055 --> 01:14:40,559
For instance here we have an 
important part of a famous financier

1178
01:14:43,562 --> 01:14:46,983
Here is the nose of the 
Chief Justice of Freiburg

1179
01:14:48,234 --> 01:14:49,652
Regrettably non Aryan

1180
01:14:50,152 --> 01:14:51,362
I made him a new one

1181
01:14:52,363 --> 01:14:54,573
Well,how do you like to 
look of some of the others

1182
01:14:54,573 --> 01:14:55,866
I mustn't disturb you

1183
01:15:04,917 --> 01:15:08,421
-Everything satisfactory,Capt?
-For the present,yes

1184
01:15:11,841 --> 01:15:12,925
Heil Hitler

1185
01:15:29,817 --> 01:15:30,860
It's true

1186
01:15:32,820 --> 01:15:34,655
Seemed so fantastic I couldn't believe it

1187
01:15:36,532 --> 01:15:40,494
This afternoon the same voice 
saying those vile,horrible things

1188
01:15:42,163 --> 01:15:44,957
Every tone,every word, told me it was you

1189
01:15:47,193 --> 01:15:48,252
Say something

1190
01:15:49,336 --> 01:15:50,546
What do you want me to say?

1191
01:15:51,172 --> 01:15:52,256
Why did you do it?

1192
01:15:53,716 --> 01:15:55,259
I did it because I had to do it

1193
01:15:57,094 --> 01:15:59,889
Because I saw people I 
love rushing to destruction

1194
01:16:01,098 --> 01:16:04,310
I saw that many who felt as I 
did were powerless as individuals

1195
01:16:04,310 --> 01:16:06,270
but if we could only find a way

1196
01:16:06,270 --> 01:16:07,888
to putting them in touch with each other

1197
01:16:07,888 --> 01:16:10,566
uniting their strength 
the disaster may be averted

1198
01:16:13,486 --> 01:16:15,196
The freedom station the way we found

1199
01:16:15,988 --> 01:16:18,282
What do you want to do? Start a revolution?

1200
01:16:18,282 --> 01:16:19,950
Yes,revolution

1201
01:16:20,659 --> 01:16:23,579
You believe that Hitler is working 
for peace,but you are wrong

1202
01:16:23,579 --> 01:16:26,874
In three days our army 
will march into Poland

1203
01:16:28,959 --> 01:16:31,670
Then I decided to tell the nation 
something of vital importance

1204
01:16:32,096 --> 01:16:33,256
Just as it was

1205
01:16:34,298 --> 01:16:35,299
I don't believe it

1206
01:16:36,133 --> 01:16:37,134
But it's true

1207
01:16:37,843 --> 01:16:39,345
Then why didn't you tell them today?

1208
01:16:39,345 --> 01:16:42,348
I was cut off before I could

1209
01:16:42,348 --> 01:16:43,724
Tonight I shall tell them

1210
01:16:45,267 --> 01:16:46,560
If it's the last thing I do

1211
01:16:46,852 --> 01:16:47,853
And it will be

1212
01:16:48,162 --> 01:16:51,482
You think you are brave but nothing 
but a fool or worse you're a traitor

1213
01:16:52,233 --> 01:16:54,151
They'll kill you and you'll deserve it

1214
01:16:54,151 --> 01:16:56,195
You haven't a chance after this afternoon

1215
01:16:56,737 --> 01:16:59,198
-I saw the Gestapo outside here
-They found nothing

1216
01:16:59,424 --> 01:17:00,491
But what about me?

1217
01:17:00,491 --> 01:17:04,245
I suppose you think I'm going to 
shield you because I'm your wife

1218
01:17:06,956 --> 01:17:09,959
No Irena I don't expect you to

1219
01:17:15,239 --> 01:17:16,298
Oh God

1220
01:17:18,509 --> 01:17:19,718
This is a nightmare

1221
01:17:20,202 --> 01:17:21,262
I want to wake up

1222
01:17:23,089 --> 01:17:25,391
Karl,what have they done to us?

1223
01:17:26,292 --> 01:17:27,351
Got us

1224
01:17:28,477 --> 01:17:29,495
everyone

1225
01:17:32,148 --> 01:17:33,399
I must go

1226
01:17:34,900 --> 01:17:35,943
Karl

1227
01:17:37,736 --> 01:17:38,737
Where are you going?

1228
01:17:41,115 --> 01:17:42,533
Please tell me I must know

1229
01:17:50,691 --> 01:17:51,750
Remember?

1230
01:17:57,840 --> 01:17:59,592
Karl,I got to talk to you

1231
01:18:00,676 --> 01:18:01,927
Irena there's no time now

1232
01:18:10,678 --> 01:18:11,770
Karl

1233
01:18:15,441 --> 01:18:16,442
What am I to do?

1234
01:18:22,540 --> 01:18:24,325
You must do what's your
conscience tells you

1235
01:18:25,367 --> 01:18:28,746
If you feel it's your duty 
to report me I shall understand

1236
01:18:30,080 --> 01:18:31,790
And you know where to tell them to find me

1237
01:18:40,216 --> 01:18:41,792
Otto what are you doing here?

1238
01:18:41,892 --> 01:18:43,219
I might ask what you're doing

1239
01:18:43,219 --> 01:18:44,294
With the freedom radio

1240
01:18:48,991 --> 01:18:50,559
Don't know what you are talking about

1241
01:18:51,035 --> 01:18:52,061
Don't you?

1242
01:18:54,021 --> 01:18:55,856
I'm going straight to Gestapo headquarters

1243
01:18:56,733 --> 01:18:57,942
Perhaps you'll understand that

1244
01:19:00,069 --> 01:19:02,488
Of course,I'm going with you

1245
01:19:02,863 --> 01:19:04,143
You'd better not

1246
01:19:04,498 --> 01:19:06,075
I warn you I shall tell them the truth

1247
01:19:06,125 --> 01:19:07,451
I shall tell them the truth

1248
01:19:08,619 --> 01:19:10,537
That'll be the end of freedom radio

1249
01:19:10,788 --> 01:19:12,039
Don't try and fool me

1250
01:19:12,039 --> 01:19:12,798
Fool you?

1251
01:19:13,257 --> 01:19:16,001
Never once I was fooling if I 
never acted well before I did then

1252
01:19:16,001 --> 01:19:17,461
You weren't acting

1253
01:19:18,262 --> 01:19:19,296
You've been crying

1254
01:19:20,172 --> 01:19:22,716
My dear child how many 
years have I been on stage?

1255
01:19:22,716 --> 01:19:25,427
And you know that one of 
the first thing that you learn

1256
01:19:25,427 --> 01:19:27,388
is to cry convincingly

1257
01:19:28,147 --> 01:19:29,974
As a matter of fact also one of the easiest

1258
01:19:30,324 --> 01:19:31,350
No one would have told me

1259
01:19:31,350 --> 01:19:33,435
whether we were going if 
I hadn't turn on the tears

1260
01:19:33,435 --> 01:19:35,220
You can say what you 
like you still love him

1261
01:19:35,220 --> 01:19:36,822
You wouldn't lift a finger against him

1262
01:19:37,898 --> 01:19:38,898
Love him

1263
01:19:39,149 --> 01:19:40,159
I hate him

1264
01:19:40,659 --> 01:19:41,902
He's a traitor

1265
01:19:43,404 --> 01:19:46,365
Played right into my hands I 
know where the freedom station is

1266
01:19:49,243 --> 01:19:50,244
Are you coming?

1267
01:19:55,758 --> 01:19:57,835
Did he give yous any hint 
as to where he's going?

1268
01:19:58,302 --> 01:19:59,962
He said he was going to Oberstad

1269
01:19:59,962 --> 01:20:01,402
He didn't say that

1270
01:20:02,756 --> 01:20:03,841
Where did he say?

1271
01:20:03,841 --> 01:20:05,259
He didn't mention any place

1272
01:20:07,052 --> 01:20:09,388
Otto couldn't have heard 
we were just outside the door

1273
01:20:11,140 --> 01:20:14,143
that's were they've gone well that 
simplifies matters a good deal

1274
01:20:14,143 --> 01:20:15,702
We should be able to get them all now

1275
01:20:16,520 --> 01:20:18,480
Well,Irena,I can't thank you enough

1276
01:20:18,480 --> 01:20:20,858
Dressler,stay where you are,I want you

1277
01:20:22,392 --> 01:20:24,862
We know of course what they 
intended to say at the meeting

1278
01:20:24,862 --> 01:20:25,862
Of what?

1279
01:20:25,930 --> 01:20:28,574
Our troops about to march into Poland

1280
01:20:28,574 --> 01:20:31,410
They know by giving the 
public a piece of news like that

1281
01:20:31,410 --> 01:20:32,953
they're creating immense difficulties

1282
01:20:33,462 --> 01:20:35,914
But it's not to,of course,we 
are not attacking Poland,are we?

1283
01:20:36,832 --> 01:20:39,126
Yes it's true enough,it was forced on us

1284
01:20:40,586 --> 01:20:42,463
Naturally you'll keep all this to yourself

1285
01:20:44,223 --> 01:20:45,257
Of course

1286
01:20:48,669 --> 01:20:51,722
Thank you again,you helped us enormously

1287
01:20:51,722 --> 01:20:53,915
I'm very glad that I helped you,
I hope you catch them

1288
01:20:54,124 --> 01:20:55,726
That won't take long now

1289
01:21:02,867 --> 01:21:03,901
Good bye

1290
01:21:07,488 --> 01:21:08,572
She was lying wasn't she?

1291
01:21:09,156 --> 01:21:11,492
-Well I
-I see you agree with me

1292
01:21:11,492 --> 01:21:12,868
She is very much in love with him

1293
01:21:12,868 --> 01:21:14,536
I do have the well meaning 
she will not get into any

1294
01:21:14,536 --> 01:21:17,039
That's all right I'll see that 
she's kept out of it

1295
01:21:17,915 --> 01:21:19,458
Tell me exactly what you heard

1296
01:21:21,126 --> 01:21:22,878
-You say he didn't mention a name?
-No,Sir

1297
01:21:23,879 --> 01:21:24,922
What did he say then?

1298
01:21:25,022 --> 01:21:26,507
She asked him where they were going

1299
01:21:26,540 --> 01:21:28,175
He didn't say anything at first

1300
01:21:28,175 --> 01:21:30,010
Then he said something about

1301
01:21:30,010 --> 01:21:31,136
"Remember?"

1302
01:21:31,136 --> 01:21:32,679
He's knocking on something

1303
01:21:34,148 --> 01:21:35,148
Like that

1304
01:21:39,570 --> 01:21:41,105
-Like that?
-Yes,Sir

1305
01:21:42,540 --> 01:21:43,607
Where were you?

1306
01:21:44,033 --> 01:21:45,150
Right behind that door,Sir

1307
01:21:48,695 --> 01:21:49,863
-That one?
-Yes,Sir

1308
01:21:50,798 --> 01:21:51,957
Where do you think he was?

1309
01:21:52,699 --> 01:21:54,451
Somewhat about here

1310
01:21:56,295 --> 01:21:57,371
Of course I can't be sure

1311
01:22:00,707 --> 01:22:01,959
No,of course not

1312
01:22:06,180 --> 01:22:07,256
Probably the desk

1313
01:22:08,757 --> 01:22:09,925
Or something on it

1314
01:22:13,387 --> 01:22:14,721
Or perhaps

1315
01:23:00,309 --> 01:23:01,477
You know where this is?

1316
01:23:08,317 --> 01:23:09,317
Yes,Sir

1317
01:23:09,376 --> 01:23:12,196
That's Herr Spiedler's cottage,
we've been there often

1318
01:23:16,233 --> 01:23:19,311
Dear Hans make sure your transmitter 
is in order in case mine breaks down

1319
01:23:19,411 --> 01:23:21,305
-It's all right I've just overhauled it
-Good

1320
01:23:23,916 --> 01:23:25,250
-Look after her
-I will

1321
01:23:31,256 --> 01:23:33,133
-Do you feel any better?
-I'll be all right

1322
01:23:35,344 --> 01:23:37,804
You know Carl I don't like this arrangement

1323
01:23:37,804 --> 01:23:38,839
What's wrong with it?

1324
01:23:38,839 --> 01:23:41,600
There's no necessity for you 
to do this broadcast alone

1325
01:23:41,600 --> 01:23:44,061
The boys can take the boat,
I'll come with you

1326
01:23:44,061 --> 01:23:45,229
Oh no that won't do

1327
01:23:45,229 --> 01:23:47,797
you got to stay with the second 
transmitter ready for tomorrow

1328
01:23:48,866 --> 01:23:51,176
Have you told me everything 
what happened this afternoon?

1329
01:23:53,512 --> 01:23:54,530
Yes I think so

1330
01:23:55,822 --> 01:23:56,822
Why?

1331
01:23:57,683 --> 01:23:58,892
No one called at the clinic?

1332
01:23:59,235 --> 01:24:03,163
Just getting interested where you'd 
been or anything like that?

1333
01:24:04,748 --> 01:24:06,875
My dear fellow what are you worrying about?

1334
01:24:06,875 --> 01:24:10,087
It never slipped up yet no 
earthly reason why we should now

1335
01:24:10,513 --> 01:24:13,465
All you got to do is to take that 
boat as far away from here as possible

1336
01:24:14,216 --> 01:24:15,592
It's a common sense precaution

1337
01:24:16,218 --> 01:24:17,761
I'll see you tomorrow as arranged

1338
01:24:53,714 --> 01:24:54,798
That'll be all thank you

1339
01:25:04,266 --> 01:25:05,266
Karl

1340
01:25:06,560 --> 01:25:07,560
Karl

1341
01:25:08,253 --> 01:25:09,329
Irena

1342
01:25:10,639 --> 01:25:12,149
Otto overheard us in the library

1343
01:25:13,108 --> 01:25:16,028
I had to go to Rabenau 
pretended to give you away

1344
01:25:16,045 --> 01:25:18,838
I said you've gone to Oberstadt,
that was all I could think what to do

1345
01:25:18,914 --> 01:25:20,415
But I don't think Otto believed me

1346
01:25:20,415 --> 01:25:21,908
and he's been here often

1347
01:25:26,538 --> 01:25:28,290
Rabenau said there's going to be a war

1348
01:25:30,959 --> 01:25:32,336
You've been right all the time

1349
01:25:33,420 --> 01:25:34,630
And I've been blind

1350
01:25:36,923 --> 01:25:37,923
Oh,Karl

1351
01:26:00,572 --> 01:26:03,075
Darling,you can't stay here

1352
01:26:03,567 --> 01:26:04,826
I've got to make the broadcast

1353
01:26:05,327 --> 01:26:06,912
I'm not going away again

1354
01:26:07,829 --> 01:26:09,081
I'm with you now

1355
01:26:09,173 --> 01:26:10,232
No,it's impossible

1356
01:26:11,541 --> 01:26:14,670
You must take the car and I'll 
meet you somewhere afterward

1357
01:26:14,670 --> 01:26:15,950
I can't do that

1358
01:26:16,046 --> 01:26:16,888
I hired one

1359
01:26:16,964 --> 01:26:18,631
in case they should be look out for mine

1360
01:26:18,631 --> 01:26:19,631
I've send it away,you see

1361
01:26:20,634 --> 01:26:21,718
Can't get rid of me

1362
01:26:23,762 --> 01:26:24,971
I am not going

1363
01:26:28,183 --> 01:26:30,352
No,you're not going

1364
01:27:13,437 --> 01:27:14,813
I wonder where's that going

1365
01:27:15,822 --> 01:27:17,566
It might be the Vienna express

1366
01:27:18,734 --> 01:27:19,734
Vienna

1367
01:27:20,485 --> 01:27:21,485
Budapest

1368
01:27:21,987 --> 01:27:22,987
Istanbul

1369
01:27:25,249 --> 01:27:27,951
How often have we seen 
that on the side of the train

1370
01:27:30,979 --> 01:27:32,873
We've never got further than Vienna

1371
01:27:35,208 --> 01:27:36,710
We never wanted to

1372
01:27:37,294 --> 01:27:38,837
We didn't did we?

1373
01:27:41,757 --> 01:27:44,657
It's time come and help 
me put up the aerial

1374
01:27:49,598 --> 01:27:50,724
I'm in the cottage now

1375
01:27:52,434 --> 01:27:53,434
No

1376
01:27:53,727 --> 01:27:55,312
But as soon as they start transmitting

1377
01:27:55,312 --> 01:27:56,888
we'll pick then up with the detectors

1378
01:27:56,989 --> 01:27:58,231
They can't have gone far

1379
01:27:58,440 --> 01:27:59,900
Report to me the moment you get them

1380
01:27:59,908 --> 01:28:01,868
The Chancellery is on 
to me every five minutes

1381
01:28:09,075 --> 01:28:10,160
They will be any moment now

1382
01:28:10,160 --> 01:28:12,871
we'd better stay here and get 
our bearings from headquarters

1383
01:28:12,871 --> 01:28:14,748
-Yes,Sir
-Wait for me in the car

1384
01:28:18,919 --> 01:28:20,295
-Finished?
-Yes

1385
01:28:45,537 --> 01:28:46,780
I'm glad you're here

1386
01:28:52,786 --> 01:28:53,786
Good luck

1387
01:28:56,014 --> 01:29:00,418
This is a German freedom station 
calling on shortwave 26.9

1388
01:29:01,753 --> 01:29:06,007
" A few hours ago we told you we had news 
of vital importance to each one of you"

1389
01:29:06,675 --> 01:29:09,261
"You may find it hard to believe"

1390
01:29:09,261 --> 01:29:10,381
Just coming in

1391
01:29:11,638 --> 01:29:12,998
There’s fatigue 97

1392
01:29:15,767 --> 01:29:17,287
Breslau bearing 205

1393
01:29:19,771 --> 01:29:23,900
"Over and over again you've been 
told that democracies will not fight"

1394
01:29:24,526 --> 01:29:29,781
"We have certain proofs that they 
will but only if you forced them to"

1395
01:29:29,781 --> 01:29:31,658
"All these things rest with you"

1396
01:29:36,079 --> 01:29:39,249
"You cannot escape responsibility 
by blaming on your leaders"

1397
01:29:39,249 --> 01:29:41,042
"if you allow this thing to happen

1398
01:29:41,042 --> 01:29:45,297
"the blame is yours and you will 
earn the loathing of posterity"

1399
01:29:46,131 --> 01:29:48,064
"You gave this man his power"

1400
01:30:17,003 --> 01:30:18,914
-Switch on the speakers
-Switch on the speakers

1401
01:30:21,082 --> 01:30:24,502
"Your future is at stake,
your lives are at stake"

1402
01:30:24,502 --> 01:30:27,964
"It is through actions united 
and courageous actions"

1403
01:30:27,964 --> 01:30:30,884
" that from our hearts we 
appeal you tonight"

1404
01:30:30,884 --> 01:30:31,909
Open these doors

1405
01:30:32,594 --> 01:30:33,594
Get down

1406
01:30:34,596 --> 01:30:37,515
"Do not deceive yourselves 
that nothing could be done"

1407
01:30:37,599 --> 01:30:38,600
"and let you act now"

1408
01:30:38,600 --> 01:30:41,770
I give you five seconds to 
stop this broadcasting,come out

1409
01:30:43,480 --> 01:30:46,358
"Unless you act now your 
chances are gone forever"

1410
01:30:47,484 --> 01:30:51,029
"No man or woman who loves 
the fatherland or fights his liberty"

1411
01:30:51,029 --> 01:30:55,533
 "can afford to stand aside,rise 
up and make our stand for freedom"

1412
01:30:55,533 --> 01:30:57,400
"make ourselves hard before"

1413
01:31:08,171 --> 01:31:09,171
Karl

1414
01:31:27,440 --> 01:31:31,653
"Did you hear that was 
the death of a brave man"

1415
01:31:32,988 --> 01:31:34,823
"he died for freedom and for Germany"

1416
01:31:36,592 --> 01:31:37,659
Come and have it again

1417
01:31:37,826 --> 01:31:39,077
No,no

1418
01:32:25,081 --> 01:32:28,585
"You have heard the last broadcast 
of the so called freedom station"

1419
01:32:29,419 --> 01:32:32,589
"Those responsible for the 
outrage have been silenced"

1420
01:32:37,135 --> 01:32:39,304
Give me the Chancellery on the telephone

1421
01:32:42,515 --> 01:32:46,853
"This is the Freedom station 
calling on wavelength 26.9 meters"

1422
01:32:48,813 --> 01:32:53,234
"we shall be broadcasting tomorrow 
night at our usual time 10 30"

1423
01:32:57,614 --> 01:32:58,948
"That is all for tonight"

1424
01:33:04,496 --> 01:33:06,176
Subtitles by Nostromo
